				<wikidot:authorName>clubby789</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3806687</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Since the clay is not dangerous until activated by a very specific sound, it isn't quite apocalyptic. However, the difficulty of tracking it means it is extremely difficult to effectively contain.</p> 
				 	]]>
